query: WITH entities AS (SELECT reference, id FROM deposits WHERE (((reference, id) > ($3, $2)) OR $2 IS NULL) ORDER BY reference, id LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: DepositId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN deposit_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.reference, i.id, i.id, e.sequence
